ancient theology of the Greeks, and to be earlier than the controversies
of the Greeks against the Latins.”

<span id="ii.xx-p10"></span>This second passage is as follows:—

<span id="ii.xx-p11"></span>“For the Spirit of God is good.  *And Thy
good Spirit*, says David, *shall lead me in the land of righteousness*. 
